gap_question_type guidance:
  mechanism   — the question asks HOW something is achieved (strategies, patterns, approaches)
  metric      — the question asks HOW MUCH or WHAT TARGET (numbers, thresholds, percentages)
  constraint  — the question asks WHAT IS NOT ALLOWED or WHAT MUST BE MET (hard limits)
  stakeholder — the question asks WHO cares, decides, or is affected
  timeline    — the question asks WHEN or HOW OFTEN (deadlines, intervals, frequencies)
  unknown     — the question intent does not clearly fall into any category
